name: LATEX GLOVES 9 INCH
description:
Latex Gloves are used in cleanrooms, which are used in FAB, LCD, BLU, HDD.
Designed to float on the tip of the finger to smooth anti-slip effect.
High resilience up to 750%, for real feeling, suitable for use in jobs that require detailed details.
Compliance with standards: ASTM D3578, Quality Management System: ISO9001: 2008.

name: PU PALM FIT GLOVES
description:
Used in assembly lines (LCD assemblies, semiconductors, cars, glasses, etc.). Electrostatic precipitations in the manufacturing and inspection of sophisticated electronics.
Using 100% nylon elastic elastic is very convenient
Polyrethuene should have a slip-resistant function, protecting hands from external impacts.

categories: Default Category/FINGER COAT - ESD FINGER COAT
name: FINGER COAT RING TYPE
description:
The finger coat are anti-static, which is commonly used in clean rooms.
Ultra cleaned and super soft. It is suitable for high precision parts such as electronic components, PCB, BLU.
The average tensile strength of this product is 24 Mpa (3480 lbs / in (2) and they have an elongation at break of 600%.
